To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private InNeck _inneck;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_inneck = InNeck(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_inneck.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "period", _inneck.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "inneck", _inneck.Current);
}
